*Dođe* veče i dan se završi. (Nightfall came and the day ended.)

*Došla* je i sjela za stol. (She came and sat at the table.)

*Dođoše* svi na proslavu. (Everyone came to the celebration.)

*Dođoh* ja prvi. (I came first.)

*Dođeše* im vijesti izdaleka. (News from afar came to them.)

*Dođe* nam vrijeme za odlazak. (It was time for us to go.)